23 professional relationship with the social worker, the social worker's license may be
24 revoked or suspended with mandatory treatment of the social worker as prescribed
25 by the board. The board may require the social worker to pay a specified amount for
26 mental health services for the client which are needed as a result of the sexual
27 contact.
